<h2>5. Best Practices & Methodology</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Check File Importance:</strong> Always review files before deletion.</li>
<li><strong>Backup Important Data:</strong> Use <strong>Time Machine</strong> or cloud storage.</li>
<li><strong>Schedule Regular Cleanup:</strong> Monthly or weekly to prevent clutter.</li>
<li><strong>Use Smart Folders & Tags:</strong> Helps organize large downloads.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Logic Flow:</strong></p>
<pre><code>
Check Downloads Folder → Identify Unnecessary Files → Backup (Optional) → Move to Trash → Empty Trash → Confirm Space Reclaimed
</code></pre>
