<h2>8. AI Tips for Automation</h2>
<ul>
<li>Use <strong>Automator</strong> or <strong>Shortcuts</strong> to auto-delete files older than X days.</li>
<li>Create a <strong>cron job</strong> to run a Terminal script weekly:</li>
</ul>
<pre><code class="language-bash">
0 9 * * 1 rm -rf ~/Downloads/*.zip
</code></pre>
<ul>
<li>AI can suggest files for deletion based on file type and last access date.</li>
</ul>
